Guide to EMPORiO's CSS Onlinepatch

1: 	Unrar the contents of the RAR to your CSS main folder 
	(make sure it didnt create a subfolder named Files or something).

2: 	Download and install Steam from www.steampowered.com
	(make sure you dont search for games, but close Steam RIGHT AWAY when you finish registring)

3:	Edit your SteamApp.cfg file that you copied from the Onlinepatch.
	It's 3 things you need to edit; 
	-the path to your CSS folder (i.e C:gamesCSS )
	-your Steam userid that you just created.
	(Here EMPORiO explained wrong about the username, it should be your SteamUserID NOT your email)
	-and your password
	Save and close the file.

4:	Launch CSS from the shortcut you allready made earlier.
